  {
    question: "Can I continue Messenger conversations myself?",
    answer: "Replying directly to a Messenger thread transfers control to you — the AI recognises your message and steps aside. You can follow up personally with pricing, material options, and site visit arrangements while the customer sees a single continuous conversation."
  },
  {
    question: "How is Messenger data handled?",
